# game-algorithms

## Core Game Mechanics

### Turn Structure
- Draw Phase: Draw 1 card (2 on first turn)
- Energy Phase: Gain +1 max Energy (cap 10)
- Main Phase: Play cards and abilities
- Combat Phase: Resolve battles
- End Phase: Cleanup and trigger effects

### Resource Systems
- Energy: Base +1/turn, cap 10
- Momentum: Gained from combat wins and card plays, cap 5

### Combat Resolution
- Speed-based initiative order
- Simultaneous damage resolution
- Unit destruction at 0 health
- Zone-specific combat rules
- Keywords: Quick Attack, Overwhelm, Lifesteal, Shield

